description: Web's Leading Site for Custom Signs
overview: We acknowledge that only you understand the intricacies of your facility and know how your signage should look like. That’s why, at MyCustomSign, we offer you an extensive range of customizable sign templates. Choose a design, add your message, upload your logo, or send us your artwork - customers have a host of options to choose from. The design is yours, but the material guarantee is ours! Our professional aluminum signs are made using 3M materials and carry a ten year warranty. Many of our signs last as long as 25 years outdoors! Reordering is easy; customers keep coming back to our site. A part of the SmartSign group, we believe that by delivering quality products, we gain a lifetime of loyalty, and you gain an economic partner for your sign needs. Worrying about cost? We don’t charge extra for customization. And our prices are less than competitors’. Get an instant custom signage quote in just seconds. If you run a non-profit organization, partner with us and we will offer custom signs for free or at discounted rates.
